item.description:
New to KubeVault? Please start here.
 VaultPolicy CRD Vault operator will create Vault Policy according to VaultPolicy CRD (CustomResourceDefinition) specification. If the user deletes the VaultPolicy CRD, then respective policy will also be deleted from Vault.
apiVersion: policy.kubevault.com/v1alpha1 kind: VaultPolicy metadata: name: &lt;name&gt; namespace: &lt;namespace&gt; spec: ... status: ...   Note: To resolve the naming conflict, name of policy in Vault will follow this format: k8s.{spec.clusterName}.{spec.namespace}.{spec.name}
